OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Andrew
OL,7,FFletcher was in court as the trio were
OL,8,Fjailed for life being convicted of
OL,9,FPaul's murder.
OL,11,FA mother who watched as her son
OL,12,Fstabbed a man to death while her
OL,13,Fdaughter filmed it for social media
OL,14,Fhas been jailed alongside her children.
OL,16,FPaul Scott, 37, was murdered on his
OL,17,Fown doorstep on 22 June 2025 after
OL,18,FJoanne Maxwell, 44, and her two
OL,19,Fchildren planned a revenge attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
