PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,FAmie Clegg, 22, lured Paul to the
OL,7,Ffront door of his home on Peridot
OL,8,FClose in Blackburn, before stepping
OL,9,Fout of the way to video her brother,
OL,10,FLiam Donlin, 25, stabbing him with a
OL,11,Fknife.
OL,13,FDespite ringing emergency services
OL,14,Fafter the attack at 3.30am, Clegg lied
OL,15,Fto the call handler about how he had
OL,16,Fsuffered his injuries, gave false
OL,17,Fnames and claimed she did not know the
OL,18,Faddress of where she was.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,FAs the call handler talked her through
OL,7,Fperforming CPR she told them Paul was
OL,8,F"already dead" and there was "nothing
OL,9,Fthey could do for him" - arguing she
OL,10,Fdid not know what she was needed to do.
OL,12,FPreston Crown Court heard how the
OL,13,Fsiblings, along with their mother
OL,14,FJoanne Maxwell, 44, turned up at
OL,15,FPaul's home, armed with knives in a
OL,16,Fplanned revenge attack after Maxwell
OL,17,Fwas involved in an altercation in
OL,18,FSeptember 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,FPaul had been present at the
OL,7,Faltercation, but his only involvement
OL,8,Fwas attempting to split it up, the
OL,9,Fcourt heard.
OL,11,FDuring the 13-day trial, the court was
OL,12,Ftold Clegg and Maxwell had sent
OL,13,Fmessages to associates threatening
OL,14,FPaul and those involved in the initial
OL,15,Faltercation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
