OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,FMaxwell received a 23-year minimum
OL,7,Fterm, Donlin was given a 26-year
OL,8,Fminimum term, and Clegg was given a 20-
OL,9,Fyear minimum term.
OL,11,FJoanna White for the Crown Prosecution
OL,12,FService said: "Encouraged by his
OL,13,Fmother, Liam Donlin stabbed Paul Scott
OL,14,Fin the chest with severe force, while
OL,15,Fhis sister, Amie Clegg filmed it.
OL,26,@tD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,F"Joanne Maxwell wanted revenge and
OL,7,Fenlisted the help of her adult
OL,8,Fchildren. The three acted together,
OL,9,Ftaking different roles, but all with
OL,10,Fthe shared intention to deliberately
OL,11,Finflict serious harm on Paul Scott.
OL,13,F"It is deeply concerning to see a
OL,14,Fmother, encouraging her own children
OL,15,Fto carry and use weapons. The Crown
OL,16,FProsecution Service will continue to
OL,17,Fwork with our partners to tackle the
OL,18,Fdevastating impact of knife crime.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
