FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1774264485
OL,3,CMum and her two children jailed for
OL,4,Cmurdering man on his doorstep
OL,6,F"I hope as Maxwell and her children
OL,7,Fface the full consequences of their
OL,8,Factions; Mr Scott's loved ones can
OL,9,Ffeel some sense of justice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]
